    "and found that the relationships still held (see SI for details).",
    "Results of this analysis could be interpreted in two ways.",
    "One way to interpret these results is that the use of a certain vocabulary, particularly that of EXPLORING HUMAN AND AI EMOTIONAL SUPPORT specific complex words, may be associated with perceived quality.",
    "Humans who use these words are then evaluated as better reappraisers merely as a result of using them.",
    "A second interpretation of these results is that there is some latent higher quality reappraisal tendency that is predicted by the use of these words."
